Setting.Name: Number of partitions for k-fold test

Comment.Text:
Use this scenario on your own risk.
This scenario can be used to initialize a classifier based on the predictions recorded in the file. Training is triggered by the number 182 (end of experiment instead of 199 as before this only allowed the first 10 letters being used for training). So this scenario will train on all trials you recorded, but use the own predictions as labels. Thus, make sure you run this script on data you recorded in free mode (free mode and without any letters in the WordToSpell field of the python frontend) and with enough repititions (e.g. 20)
The predictions should start from 1 if they start from zero it will not work (so only newly recorded files which record the predictions starting from 1 will work with this)
